{"id":2043,"date":"2020-08-24T22:32:26","date_gmt":"2020-08-24T15:32:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=2043"},"modified":"2021-03-01T17:43:37","modified_gmt":"2021-03-01T10:43:37","slug":"newsletter-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/newsletter-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Newsletter"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47h47soo fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Wonderful-Womens-World.jpg\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48j9ppbh fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48j9ppbi fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-4bu453u0 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">TU\u1ea6N L\u1ec4 CHO PH\u00c1I \u0110\u1eb8P \u0110\u1ea6Y M\u00c0U S\u1eaeC<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-4bu456o1 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">K&iacute;nh g\u1eedi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch,<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi th&aacute;ng Ba, Gia \u0111&igrave;nh Caravelle \u0111&atilde; chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh &amp; \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i \u0111\u1ec3 Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&agrave;nh t\u1eb7ng s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, m\u1ed9t ch&uacute;t tinh t\u1ebf v&agrave; nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u y&ecirc;u th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh. V\u1edbi t&acirc;m \u0111i\u1ec3m d&agrave;nh cho ng&agrave;y Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf Ph\u1ee5 N\u1eef, 8\/3, c&aacute;c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh c\u1ee7a Caravelle Saigon s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp trung v&agrave;o tu\u1ea7n l\u1ec5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v&agrave; sau ng&agrave;y l\u1ec5 v\u1edbi g&oacute;i ph&ograve;ng \u1edf l&atilde;ng m\u1ea1n, \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i n&acirc;ng c\u1ea5p l&ecirc;n Suite mi\u1ec5n ph&iacute;, tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Spa th&iacute;ch th&uacute; v&agrave; nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ea8m th\u1ef1c c&oacute; th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l&agrave; ch\u1ea5t x&uacute;c t&aacute;c cho t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t. H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh th&aacute;ng Ba t\u1ea1i Caravelle Saigon s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c&aacute;c Qu&yacute; c&ocirc; xuy&ecirc;n su\u1ed1t c&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng gian \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n. \u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n l&agrave; Caf&eacute; de l&rsquo;Opera v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n Tr&agrave; chi\u1ec1u m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t Tapas Kitchen lu&ocirc;n l&agrave;m b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ef1c kh&aacute;ch. Sau \u0111&oacute; ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng Reflections v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc v&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng ch\u0103m ch&uacute;t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m gi&aacute; r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang v&agrave;o th\u1ee9 T\u01b0. V&agrave; cu\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c Qu&yacute; c&ocirc; c&oacute; th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec7c buffet t\u1ed1i hay tr\u01b0a Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7y \u1eafp m&oacute;n ngon c\u1ee7a Nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng Nineteen.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi tr&ecirc;n ch\u1ec9 l&agrave; &yacute; ngh\u0129 tho&aacute;ng qua, h&atilde;y \u0111\u1ebfn v&agrave; c&ugrave;ng Caravelle Saigon chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch. Gia \u0111&igrave;nh Caravelle r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch&agrave;o \u0111&oacute;n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i trung t&acirc;m th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 ph\u1ed3n hoa n&agrave;y.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Tr&acirc;n tr\u1ecdng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle Saigon<\/em><\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48j9ppbh{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-4bu456o1 ,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-4bu456o1{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-4bu456o1:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:focus,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-4bu456o1{ font-size: 16px !important;line-height: 24px !important;font-weight: normal !important;}.ffb-id-4bu456o1 ,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:focus,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:focus{ font-size: 16px !important;line-height: 24px !important;font-weight: normal !important;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-4bu456o1{ font-size: 16px !important;}}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-4bu456o1 ,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:focus,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:focus{ font-size: 16px !important;}}@media (min-width:992px) { .ffb-id-4bu456o1{ font-size: 16px !important;}}@media (min-width:992px) { .ffb-id-4bu456o1 ,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:after,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:hover,.ffb-id-4bu456o1:focus,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:before,.ffb-id-4bu456o1 *:a